  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.6.5">
<l>koḷkaiko ḷāmaiyi lātā</l>
<l>ṉeḷkali rākami lātāṉ</l>
<l>viḷkaiviḷ ḷāmaivi rumpi</l>
<l>yuḷkalan tārkkō ramutē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one without tenet [or] non-tenet,</l>
<l>the one without a passion for deriding [others],</l>
<l>desirous of not breaking what may unfold</l>
<l>for those confused in mind [he is] the one ambrosia.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
